/** * Author(s) of this code: * * Joven Manikiza */ import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Table, Link, Heading, Main, SectionBreak, Pagination } from 'govuk-react'; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import Navigation from '../../Components/Navigation'; function Profile() { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [data, setData] = useState({}); useEffect(() => { fetch('http://localhost:4000/getData.php') .then(response => response.json()) .then(data => { setData({ fullName: data[0].Forename + ' ' + data[0].Surname, dob: new Date(data[0].PersonDOB).toLocaleDateString('en-GB', { day: 'numeric', month: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' }), gender: data[0].GenderCode === '1' ? 'MALE' : 'FEMALE', address: data[0].Postcode, email: data[0].EmailAddress, contact: data[0].PhoneNumber }); }) .catch(error => console.error(error)); }, []); const formattedNumber = data[0].PhoneNumber.padStart(11, '0'); return (
navigate("/Patient")} previousPage> Back to start navigate("/GPServices")} nextPage> GP Services Profile Name {data.fullName} navigate("/NameChangeStart")} children="Change"/> D.O.B {data.dob} navigate("/DOBChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Gender {data.gender} navigate("/GenderChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Address {data.address} navigate("/AddressChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Email {data.email} navigate("/EmailChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Contact No. {} navigate("/NumberChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Password ************* navigate("/PasswordChangeStart")} children="Change"/>
); } export default Profile;
